snippet.title: PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark is out now on Steam!

The wait is over! Step into the shadows and uncover the mysteries of PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark. Explore, solve, and survive in a world where light is your only ally.

Don’t wait, dive into the darkness now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2919230
